descript.abstract: This line data layer represents roads for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Milwaukee_Roads_2015.gdb.
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
descript.supplinf: Best known date is February 27, 2015. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://county.milwaukee.gov/mclio/geodata.html.
